GreenParking EV Network is the first cross border charging network in the region.

Our App lets you:
- find the nearest station;
- check the status;
- see the location details;
- navigate to the selected station;
- register with our network to receive an access card;
- contact us for support or any clarifications. 

GreenParking EV chargers support all known electric vehicles, available on the market.
Please note that all chargers are equipped with Type2 sockets, so kindly carry your own cable to charge.

For the past 20 years, GreenParking has provided comprehensive parking services and innovative solutions to over 100 sites across the UAE and Middle East. By introducing state of the art technologies and environmentally friendly solutions, its aim is to consistently challenge and improve the parking industry. GreenParking believes that there is no reason parking cannot be green, and that through technologies such as ParkChip instead of paper ticket, contactless payments and Electric Vehicle chargers, it can contribute to a cleaner and safer environment.

GreenParking’s aim is to make the parking experience as smooth and seamless as possible for both the customer and the service provider. As industry influencer, it has always stayed ahead of the curve with its products, servicing a wide range of sectors from airports to hotels. GreenParking’s priority is to lead the way in making the Middle East a region that has more focus on green technologies, and it is constantly striving for efficient and eco-friendly solutions. 

Ranked 8th out of 100 best performing SMEs at the latest Dubai 100 SME Award, GreenParking prides itself on being the most forward-thinking parking provider in the UAE, with a strong sense of corporate responsibility. When it comes to parking in the UAE, the future certainly looks greener!
